"Set the given value for the given key only if current value for the same key "
"is lower than value. If there is no current value for the given key, the "
"value is always set."
msgstr ""
"仅在同一键的当前值小于值时设置给定的键值。 如果给定的键值没有当前值，则该值总"
"是被设置的。"

